---
title: "Folienverpackung"
title_image: /assets/img/sectors/folienverpackung.jpg
layout: layout/page-wrapper-with-breadcrumbs.njk
---

<div class="relative grow-1 flex justify-center mt-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto aspect-video min-h-120">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0d2642] z-10 opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 sm:left-20 lg:bottom-20 lg:left-20 z-10 text-white">
        <p class=" font-bold z-20 font-headline text-5xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl max-w-md md:max-w-xl mb-7 tracking-[-0.01rem]">{{ title }}</p>
        <p class="max-w-xs md:max-w-md lg:max-w-lg md:text-xl mb-6 font-bold">
             Produkte zuverlässig schützen und Ressourcen sparen</p>
        <div>
            <button class=" bg-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm md:text-base text-primary cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors">Zu den Maschinen</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <img src="{{ title_image | url }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="relative  w-full h-full object-cover bg-center z-0" loading="lazy"/>
</div>
<div class=" max-w-7xl mx-auto p-12 md:pt-24">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-6 md:mb-8 md:mt-0 pb-12 py-6 md:pb-10">
        <div
            class=" text-foreground max-w-7xl  flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-8 lg:gap-20 justify-center">
            <div class="w-fit">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-headline font-semibold md:font-bold text-foreground-headline pb-4 tracking-tight">
                    Was ist Folienverpacking?</h1>
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base text-foreground max-w-lg pb-3 tracking-wide md:tracking-normal">
                    Folienverpackungen gehören zu den am weitesten verbreiteten Verpackungsarten weltweit. Sie bestehen überwiegend aus
                    Kunststofffolien, die je nach Einsatzgebiet unterschiedliche Materialeigenschaften aufweisen.
                </p>
                <p class="leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base text-foreground max-w-lg tracking-wide md:tracking-normal">
                    Typische Kunststoffe sind Polyethylen (PE), Polypropylen (PP), Polyethylenterephthalat (PET) oder Mehrschichtverbunde,
                    die mehrere Lagen kombinieren, um optimale Barriere- und Schutzeigenschaften zu erzielen.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-md w-full hidden md:block">
                <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-cover bg-center bg-[url({{ title_image | url }})] z-10 rounded-lg"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#f5f5f5] max-w-7xl w-fit mx-auto md:mx-initial md:w-full gap-24 flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row text-[#123456] p-10 md:justify-evenly">
        <div class="max-w-[200px] w-full text-center">
            <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="lucide lucide-shield-check-icon lucide-shield-check size-9 mx-auto mb-3"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0
                    1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium">Produktschutz</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-[200px] w-full text-center">
            <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="lucide lucide-sprout-icon lucide-sprout size-9 mx-auto mb-3"><path d="M14 9.536V7a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V5a4 4 0 0 1-4 4 4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 2 1 3 1 5a5 5 0 0 1-1 3"/><path d="M4 9a5 5 0 0 1 8 4 5 5 0 0 1-8-4"/><path d="M5 21h14"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium">Nachhaltigkeit</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-[200px] w-full text-center">
            <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="lucide lucide-clock-arrow-up-icon lucide-clock-arrow-up size-9 mx-auto mb-3"><path d="M12 6v6l1.56.78"/><path d="M13.227 21.925a10 10 0 1 1 8.767-9.588"/><path d="m14 18 4-4 4 4"/><path d="M18 22v-8"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-xl font-medium">Lange Haltbarkeit</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="">
        <div class=" grow-1 flex justify-center  mb-8 md:hidden pt-12">
            <img src="{{ title_image | url }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover bg-center max-h-96 rounded-lg" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-20 px-4 pb-8 md:py-20 ">
            <div class="max-w-md w-full hidden md:block">
                <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-cover bg-center bg-[url({{ title_image | url }})] z-10 rounded-lg"></div>
            </div>
            <div class=" ">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-foreground-headline md:text-secondary-headline font-bold pb-4 ">Funktion und
                    Vorteile</h2>
                <p class=" max-w-lg text-sm md:text-base text-secondary-foreground font-light">Der Hauptzweck von Folienverpackungen
                    besteht darin, Produkte während Lagerung und Transport zu schützen. Sie bieten eine wirksame Barriere gegen
                    Feuchtigkeit, Sauerstoff, Schmutz sowie mechanische Einflüsse.</P>
                <br/>
                <p class="max-w-lg text-sm md:text-base text-secondary-foreground font-light">
                    Dadurch verlängern sie die Haltbarkeit vieler Lebensmittel erheblich und tragen zur Reduzierung von Lebensmittelabfällen
                    bei. Zudem sind Folienverpackungen leicht, flexibel und lassen sich platzsparend transportieren, was Ressourcen und
                    Energie spart.</p>
            </div>
            {#  <div class=" grow-1 justify-center items-center  hidden md:flex ">
                            <img src="{{ title_image | url }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover bg-center  max-h-72 max-w-lg rounded-lg" loading="lazy"/>
                        </div> #}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:mt-14 md:mb-12">
    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-foreground-headline font-bold text-center">Unsere Lösungen im Bereich Folienverpackung</h3>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 my-6 px-10 sm:px-16 md:px-6 xl:px-0 gap-12 md:gap-12 lg:gap-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto md:mb-20">
    {% for subdivision in collections['folienverpackung'] %}
        <div class="flex flex-col group overflow-hidden hover:z-10 md:basis-1/3 grow-1 focus:outline-hidden 
                duration-300 ease-in-out ">
            <div class=" overflow-hidden bg-[#eee] rounded-lg">
                <img class="size-full top-0 start-0 object-cover h-[350px]" src="{{ subdivision.data.image | url }}" alt="Card Image"/>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 pb-8 rounded  flex flex-col mt-4 gap-6 justify-between flex-1">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold font-headline text-foreground-headline leading-snug mb-4">
                        {{ subdivision.data.name }}
                    </h3>
                    <p class=" text-foreground text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-light">
                        {{ subdivision.data.description }}
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ page.url | url }}{{ subdivision.data.subfolder }}/" class=" flex items-center  py-3 px-6 font-semibold text-sm md:text-body-sm  tracking-wider gap-x-1 mt-1 md:mt-2  rounded-full text-primary border-2 border-primary w-fit  hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors cursor-pointer  focus:outline-hidden focus:bg-primary disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none">
                    Maschinen ansehen
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-chevron-right-icon lucide-chevron-right size-4 stroke-3"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>